snippet.title: CarX Street - Official Speedway Update 1.4.0 Trailer
snippet.description:
CarX Street - Official Speedway Update 1.4.0 Trailer.

New Sunset Speedway location now available in CarX Street with the latest update 1.4.0! 

Get ready for new fast and winding roads on the track and dive into real sports competition with the new Speedstars Energy club!

The update features a new livery editor! 
Create your unique style and show your individuality in the world of CarX Street with the new photo mode with Drone camera.

 Also, 7 new cars, 8 special offers, and new rims are introduced!Speedway Update 1.4.0 is already available for download!

Are you ready to race? Let’s rock!

Download now:

App Store® - https://apps.apple.com/us/app/carx-street/id1458863319
Google Play™ - https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.carxtech.sr&pcampaignid=web_share

Social Media:

Twitter: https://twitter.com/carx_technology
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/carx_tech
Facebook (CarX Street): https://www.facebook.com/carxstreet
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/carx2/
CarX Store: https://carx-store.com/
